ics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 394, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999201513590585, \"rank\": 7.887640877974838e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were edged out by China's Yang Hao and Lian Junjie.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6068974579964159, \"rank\": 0.6232356719771475, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"score\": 0.5916864370255184, \"rank\": 0.40495867768596194, \"text\": \"Yang Hao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\"}, {\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lian Junjie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The duo put pressure on China's pair but could not outclass them.The arena erupted with cheers after Daley and Williams scored an impressive 93.96 in their fourth dive.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6068974579964159, \"rank\": 0.6232356719771475, \"text\":